'''Masasa Lindiwe Mbangeni''' ni umukinnyi wa firime muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]  . Azwi cyane ku ruhare rwe nka ''Thembeka Shezi'' muri televiziyo izwi cyane ya ''Scandal!'' . <ref>http://www.702.co.za/articles/239838/actress-lorcia-cooper-swaps-dance-moves-for-prison-life</ref>

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Yavutse ku ya 6 Werurwe 1987 i Port Elizabeth, muri Afurika y'Epfo. Nyuma yaje kwimukira i Johannesburg kugira ngo yige. 

== Umwuga ==
Yabonye buruse ya Mandela Rhodes yo kwiga muri kaminuza ya Witwatersrand nyuma arangiza impamyabumenyi ye ya Bachelor of Arts Degree muri Dramatic Arts kabuhariwe mu kwerekana no kuyobora. Yagize yakinnye Umushyitsi ku serials televiziyo ebyiri: nk'uko 'Eunice' ku BBC icyaha drama ''Akira Abahamya'' kandi 'wungirije bwite Jackie wa' ku soapie M-Net, ''Egoli.'' ''Yakinnye kandi mu makinamico'' atatu kuri Theatre yisoko ya Johannesburg: Nogogo, ''Sundjata'' na ''Amen Corner'', iyobowe na James Ngcobo. Hagati aho, yazengurutse iserukiramuco rya Grahamstown hamwe ''n’ikinamico Oedipus @ Koonu'' . 

Muri 2013, yinjiye mu bakinnyi ba televiziyo izwi cyane ya ''Scandal!'' kandi yakinnye nka 'Thembeka Shezi'. <ref>https://www.msn.com/en-za/entertainment/local/masasa-mbangeni-reluctant-to-return-to-scandal-due-to-imposter-syndrome/ar-BB108b0i</ref> Uruhare rwamenyekanye cyane, nubwo, yavuye ku nshingano mu 2016. <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2020-06-12-masasa-mbangeni-hits-back-at-claims-scandal-will-go-downhill-without-her/</ref> Icyakora, yahawe ibihembo bibiri byumukinnyi witwaye neza mu Isabune ya TV yakuye muri South African Film and Television Awards (SAFTA) muri 2014 na 2015 kubera uruhare. Muri icyo gihe, yahawe igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza muri DStv Mzansi Magic Viewers Choice Award . Nyuma ya ''Scandal!'', yagaragaye muri saison ebyiri za ''serivise za'' tereviziyo ya Thola kuri televiziyo SABC2. Hanyuma yakinnye nka 'Celia' murukurikirane rwo ''Gusarura'' .  Nyuma yaho asubira biganiro hanyuma Inyuguti yarashwe bapfuye, gufata Mbangeni wa gusohoka kabiri mu kwerekana. <ref>https://sundayworld.co.za/news/masasa-mbangenis-second-exit-from-scandal/</ref> <ref>https://www.iol.co.za/entertainment/tv/soapies/mzansi-mourns-thembeka-shezi-as-masasa-mbangeni-exits-scandal-49254567</ref> <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/etv-on-masasa-mbangenis-exit-she-has-enjoyed-a-great-run-with-the-scandal-family-20200612</ref>

Muri 2011, yakinnye muri firime ya ''Machine Gun Preacher'' . Usibye gukina, yitabiriye ubukangurambaga bwambaye ubusa bwa Marie Claire mu 2015 hagamijwe gukangurira abaturage ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina rikorerwa abagore n'abana. 

